  "texts": [
    "Meanwhile, the null hypothesis considered to be tested is that there is not any difference between the two features using alpha = 0.05.",
    "The aim is to show that if there is no difference, then the outcome of the TwinCNN fusion model is not relevant.",
    "However, where a difference exists, then it implies that outcome from the fusion of the two modalities as reported by our experimentation is very valid.",
    "First, an F-test to check the equality of the two modalities was analyzed as reported on Table 6.",
    "Results obtained showed that F > F Critical one-tail, therefore leading to the rejection of the consideration that both modalities are equal."
  ]
}